Package com.textcontrol.reportingcloud

Contains classes and enumerations of the Text Control ReportingCloud Java wrapper.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountSettings
    Represents ReportingCloud account settings.
    FindAndReplaceBody
    Used to pass data to the find and replace method.
    MergeBlock
    Represents a merge block in a document template.
    MergeBody
    Used to pass data to the merge method.
    MergeField
    Represents a merge field in a document template.
    MergeSettings
    Holds the merge settings needed by the merge method.
    ReportingCloud
    The ReportingCloud API wrapper class.
    Template
    Holds information about a template in the template storage.
    TemplateInfo
    Holds information about the merge blocks and merge fields in a template.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ImageFormat
    This enum lists all possible image formats for the thumbnails
    ReturnFormat
    This enum lists all possible return formats for the Merge method.
